longBusinessSummary: Yashili International Holdings Ltd, an investment holding company, engages in manufacture and sale of dairy and nourishment products in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates through four segments: Milk Powder Products; Other Milk Powder Products; Dissolvable Products; and Other Operations. The company provides infant milk formula products under the Yashily, Reeborne, Dumex, Doraler, and M8 brand names. It also offers adult milk powder products under the Mengniu brand name; children milk powder under the Mengniu 1.88M brand; student milk powder under the Huicongming brand; and milk formula for the middle-aged and elderly under the Yourui brand name. In addition, the company provides various dissolvable products, such as soymilk powder, rice flour, and cereal products; and fruit oatmeal and goji drinks. Further, it is involved in the wholesale, retail, import, and export of dairy products and related materials. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. Yashili International Holdings Ltd operates as a subsidiary of China Mengniu Dairy Company Limited.
